Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    cz.cvut.fel.dbs.smartorchestra.gui.EventDetails.getFieldBeginsTime()
    As of SmartOrchestra 1.0, because the string value of mixed date and time is used in EventDetails.getFieldBeginsDate(). The method is left there for further development.
    cz.cvut.fel.dbs.smartorchestra.gui.EventDetails.getFieldEndsTime()
    As of SmartOrchestra 1.0, because the string value of mixed date and time is used in EventDetails.getFieldEndsDate(). The method is left there for further development.
    cz.cvut.fel.dbs.smartorchestra.gui.EventDetails.getInfoBeginsTime()
    As of SmartOrchestra 1.0, because the string value of mixed date and time is used in EventDetails.getFieldBeginsDate(). Use EventDetails.getInfoBeginsDate() instead.
    cz.cvut.fel.dbs.smartorchestra.gui.EventDetails.getInfoEndsTime()
    As of SmartOrchestra 1.0, because the string value of mixed date and time is used in EventDetails.getFieldEndsDate(). Use EventDetails.getInfoEndsDate() instead.
